===Etymology===
{{w|Li Shizhen}} relates {{zh-l|旄|banner}} to pronunciation ''máo'' of {{zh-l|*牦}}／{{zh-l|*犛|yak}}; he also sees a possible connection of both to {{zh-l|毛|hair}} (''{{w|Bencao Gangmu}}'', [[w:zh:s:本草綱目_(四庫全書本)/卷51上#牦牛|51A]])

However, see {{zh-l|犛}} for alternative etymology.

